<h2>Nutrition Plans for Different Body Types</h2>

<p>Choose your body type to view the nutrition plan:</p>

<ul>
    <li>
        <a href="/ectomorph">Ectomorph</a>
        <p>Athletic body type with a fast metabolism. Typically characterized by lean muscle mass and difficulty gaining weight.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
        <a href="/mesomorph">Mesomorph</a>
        <p>Naturally muscular and athletic build. Mesomorphs tend to gain and lose weight easily, with a moderate metabolism.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
        <a href="/endomorph">Endomorph</a>
        <p>Naturally stocky or rounder body type with a slower metabolism. Endomorphs may find it easier to gain weight and muscle but may struggle to lose fat.</p>
    </li>
</ul>
